    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>After spending the casting time tracing magical pathways within a precious gemstone, you touch a Huge or smaller &amp;Reference[beast]{beast} or &amp;Reference[plant]{plant}. The target must have either no &amp;Reference[int]{Intelligence} score or an &amp;Reference[int]{Intelligence} of 3 or less. The target gains an &amp;Reference[int]{Intelligence} of 10. The target also gains the ability to speak one language you know. If the target is a &amp;Reference[plant]{plant}, it gains the ability to move its limbs, roots, vines, creepers, and so forth, and it gains senses similar to a human's. Your GM chooses statistics appropriate for the awakened &amp;Reference[plant]{plant}, such as the statistics for the awakened shrub or the awakened tree.</p>\n<p>The awakened &amp;Reference[beast]{beast} or &amp;Reference[plant]{plant} is &amp;Reference[charmed]{charmed} by you for 30 days or until you or your companions do anything harmful to it. When the &amp;Reference[charmed]{charmed} condition ends, the awakened creature chooses whether to remain friendly to you, based on how you treated it while it was &amp;Reference[charmed]{charmed}.</p>\n</div>",
      "chat": ""
    },
